[
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st> <st data-num=\"03254\" class=\"\">again</st> <st data-num=\"02734\" class=\"\">raged</st> against <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, and he <st data-num=\"05496\" class=\"\">incited</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> against them, <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Go</st> <st data-num=\"04487\" class=\"\">count</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> and <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">told</st> <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st>, the <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">general in command</st> of <st data-num=\"0834 0854\">his</st> <st data-num=\"02428\" class=\"\">army</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07751 04994\">Go through</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"07626\" class=\"\">tribes</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> from <st data-num=\"01835\" class=\"\">Dan</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"0884\" class=\"\">Beer Sheba</st> and <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">muster</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st>, so I may <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> the <st data-num=\"04557\" class=\"\">size</st> of the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>, \u201cMay the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"03254 0413\">make</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> a <st data-num=\"03967\" class=\"\">hundred</st> <st data-num=\"06471\" class=\"\">times</st> <st data-num=\"01992 01992\">larger</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">right before</st> the <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st> of my <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">lord</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>! But <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">why</st> does my <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">master</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"02654\" class=\"\">want</st> to do <st data-num=\"01697 02088\">this</st>?\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">But the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">edict</st> <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">stood</st>, <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">despite</st> the objections of<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">and</st> the <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">leaders</st> of the <st data-num=\"02428\" class=\"\">army</st>. So <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> and the <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">leaders</st> of the <st data-num=\"02428\" class=\"\">army</st> <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">left</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">presence</st> in order to <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">muster</st> the <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israelite</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">They <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">crossed</st> the <st data-num=\"03383\" class=\"\">Jordan</st> and <st data-num=\"02583\" class=\"\">camped</st> at <st data-num=\"06177\" class=\"\">Aroer</st>, on the <st data-num=\"03225\" class=\"\">south side</st> of the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st>, <st data-num=\"0834 08432\">at</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"05158\" class=\"\">wadi</st> of <st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st>, <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">near</st> <st data-num=\"03270\" class=\"\">Jazer</st>. ",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "Then they <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">went on</st> to <st data-num=\"01568\" class=\"\">Gilead</st> and <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">region</st> of <st data-num=\"08483\" class=\"\">Tahtim Hodshi</st>, <st data-num=\"0935\">coming to</st> <st data-num=\"01842\" class=\"\">Dan Jaan</st> and <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">on around</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"06721\" class=\"\">Sidon</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "Then they <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">went to</st> the <st data-num=\"04013\" class=\"\">fortress</st> of <st data-num=\"06865\" class=\"\">Tyre</st><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> of the <st data-num=\"02340\" class=\"\">Hivites</st> and the <st data-num=\"03669\" class=\"\">Canaanites</st>. Then they <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">went on</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"05045\" class=\"\">Negev</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>, to <st data-num=\"0884\" class=\"\">Beer Sheba</st>. ",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"07751\" class=\"\">went through</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> and <st data-num=\"07097\" class=\"\">after</st> <st data-num=\"08672\" class=\"\">nine</st> <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">months</st> and <st data-num=\"06242\" class=\"\">twenty</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> back <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">reported</st> the <st data-num=\"04557 04662\">number</st> of <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">warriors</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>. In <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> there <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">were</st> <st data-num=\"08083 03967 0505\">800,000</st> <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st>-<st data-num=\"08025\" class=\"\">wielding</st> <st data-num=\"0376 02428\">warriors</st>, and in <st data-num=\"0376 03063\">Judah</st> there were <st data-num=\"02568 03967 0505\">500,000</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">soldiers</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">felt</st> <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">guilty</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0310 03651\">after</st> he had <st data-num=\"05608\" class=\"\">numbered</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st>. <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, \u201cI have <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">sinned</st> <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">greatly</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">by</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">doing</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">this</st>! <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st>, O <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"04994\" class=\"\">please</st> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">remove</st> the <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">guilt</st> of your <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> I have <st data-num=\"05528\" class=\"\">acted</st> <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">very</st> <st data-num=\"05528\" class=\"\">foolishly</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">got up</st> the next <st data-num=\"01242\" class=\"\">morning</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> had already <st data-num=\"01961 0559\">come</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophet</st> <st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st>, <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"02374\" class=\"\">seer</st>: ",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "\u201c<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Go</st>, <st data-num=\"01696 0413\">tell</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>: <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> am <st data-num=\"05190 05921\">offering</st> you <st data-num=\"07969\" class=\"\">three</st> forms of judgment. <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">Pick</st> <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">one</st> of <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">them</st> and I will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">carry</st> it <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">out</st> against you.\u2019\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">went</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> and <st data-num=\"05046 0559\">told</st> him, \u201cShall <st data-num=\"07651\" class=\"\">seven</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st> of <st data-num=\"07458\" class=\"\">famine</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> upon your <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>? <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Or</st> shall you <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">flee</st> for <st data-num=\"07969\" class=\"\">three</st> <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">months</st> <st data-num=\"06440\">from</st> your <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">enemies</st> with <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">them</st> in <st data-num=\"07291\" class=\"\">hot pursuit</st>? <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Or</st> shall there <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"07969\" class=\"\">three</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st> of <st data-num=\"01698\" class=\"\">plague</st> in your <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>? <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st> <st data-num=\"03045 07200\">decide</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">what</st> I should <st data-num=\"07725 01697\">tell</st> the one who <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> me.\u201d",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st>, \u201cI am <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">very</st> <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">upset</st>! I <st data-num=\"04994\" class=\"\">prefer</st> that we be <st data-num=\"05307 03027\">attacked</st> by the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> his <st data-num=\"07356\" class=\"\">mercy</st> is <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">great;</st> I do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> want to be <st data-num=\"05307 03027\">attacked</st> by <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">human hands</st>!\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">sent</st> a <st data-num=\"01698\" class=\"\">plague</st> through <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> from the <st data-num=\"01242\" class=\"\">morning</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">until</st> the completion of the <st data-num=\"04150\" class=\"\">appointed</st> <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st>, and <st data-num=\"07657 0505\" class=\"\">70,000</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"04191 04480 05971\">died</st> from <st data-num=\"01835\" class=\"\">Dan</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"0884\" class=\"\">Beer Sheba</st>. ",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "When the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">angel</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">extended</st> his <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> to <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroy</st> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">relented</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">from</st> his <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">judgment</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> He <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">told</st> the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">angel</st> who was <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">killing</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>, \u201cThat\u2019s <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">enough</st>! <st data-num=\"07503 03027\">Stop</st> <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st>!\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> (Now the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">angel</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">near</st> the <st data-num=\"01637\" class=\"\">threshing floor</st> of <st data-num=\"0728\" class=\"\">Araunah</st> the <st data-num=\"02983\" class=\"\">Jebusite</st>.) </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When he <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">angel</st> who was <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">destroying</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>, <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559 0559\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, \u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>, it is <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> who have <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">sinned</st> <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"05753\" class=\"\">done</st> this <st data-num=\"05753\" class=\"\">evil</st> thing! As for <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these</st> <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">sheep</st>\u2014<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">what</st> have they <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st>? <st data-num=\"01961 04994 03027\">Attack</st> me and my <st data-num=\"01004 01\">family</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So <st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">went</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">told</st> him, \u201c<st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">Go up</st> and <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">build</st> an <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> on the <st data-num=\"01637\" class=\"\">threshing floor</st> of <st data-num=\"0728\" class=\"\">Araunah</st> the <st data-num=\"02983\" class=\"\">Jebusite</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">went up</st> as <st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">instructed</st> him to do, <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">according to</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">instructions</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When <st data-num=\"0728\" class=\"\">Araunah</st> <st data-num=\"08259\" class=\"\">looked out</st> and <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> and his <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servants</st> <st data-num=\"05674 05921\">approaching</st> him, <st data-num=\"0728\" class=\"\">he</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">went out</st> and <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">bowed</st> to the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> with his <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">face</st><n id=\"2\" /> to the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st>. ",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0728\" class=\"\">Araunah</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04069\" class=\"\">Why</st> has my <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">lord</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> his <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st>?\u201d <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cTo <st data-num=\"07069\" class=\"\">buy</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">from</st> you the <st data-num=\"01637\" class=\"\">threshing floor</st> so I can <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">build</st> an <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, so that the <st data-num=\"04046\" class=\"\">plague</st> may be <st data-num=\"06113\" class=\"\">removed</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0728\" class=\"\">Araunah</st> <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">told</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, \u201cMy <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">lord</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> may <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">take</st> <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">whatever</st> he <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">wishes</st><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">offer</st> it. <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">Look</st>! Here are <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">oxen</st> for <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt offerings</st>, and <st data-num=\"04173\" class=\"\">threshing sledges</st><n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"03627 01241\">harnesses</st><n id=\"3\" /> for <st data-num=\"06086\" class=\"\">wood</st>. ",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "I, the <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st> of my <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">lord</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>, <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">give</st> it <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> to the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>!\u201d <st data-num=\"0728\" class=\"\">Araunah</st> also <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">told</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>, \u201cMay the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"07521\" class=\"\">show</st> you <st data-num=\"07521\" class=\"\">favor</st>!\u201d ",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "But the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"0728\" class=\"\">Araunah</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">No</st>, I <st data-num=\"03588 07069\">insist on</st> <st data-num=\"07069 04242\">buying</st> it <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">from</st> you! I will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">offer</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> my <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st> that cost me <st data-num=\"02600\" class=\"\">nothing</st>.\u201d<p class=\"bodytext\">So <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"07069\" class=\"\">bought</st> the <st data-num=\"01637\" class=\"\">threshing floor</st> and the <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">oxen</st> for <st data-num=\"02572\" class=\"\">50</st> <st data-num=\"08255\" class=\"\">pieces</st> of <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "24",
    "text": "Then <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">built</st> an <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st> and <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">offered</st> <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st> and <st data-num=\"08002\" class=\"\">peace offerings</st>. And the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"06279\" class=\"\">accepted prayers</st> for the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>, and the <st data-num=\"04046\" class=\"\">plague</st> was <st data-num=\"06113\" class=\"\">removed</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">from</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  }
]